Overview of what are the most commonly used languages and tools are used in data science sector.
This course will give you a comprehensive overview of the tools you will interact with through out of your data science career.

My take from this course:
1. Master a programming language, my recommendation is Python
2. You need to know atleast 3 programming languages including Pyhton. I'll recommend you R and SAS.
3. You will use tools like Hadoop, Apache Spark so after completing the certification, get yourself introduced to the tools.
4. Always keep yourself busy in competitions. Kaggle competitions are very helpful as you will face many problems, solving them are fun.
